item.title: CVE-2024-21983|2024-06-07T15:58:32.902Z -- netapp -- storagegrid
item.description: StorageGRID (formerly StorageGRID Webscale) versions prior to 11.8 are susceptible to a Denial of Service (DoS) vulnerability. Successful exploit by an authenticated attacker could lead to an out of memory condition or node reboot.

item.title: CVE-2024-21990|2024-04-17T19:35:23.599Z -- netapp -- ontap%20select%20deploy%20administration%20utility
item.description: ONTAP Select Deploy administration utility versions 9.12.1.x, 9.13.1.x and 9.14.1.x contain hard-coded credentials that could allow an attacker to view Deploy configuration information and modify the account credentials.
